{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC05_KEI_610.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x31,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "The sky is...so vast. I feel like I'll get sucked in if I keep looking up."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x13,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "What are you doing here with that foolish expression on your face?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Oh, hello.<CR>...I was just looking up at the sky."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x17,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Hmm... Is it really that interesting?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "I never get bored by looking up at the floating islands and flowing clouds."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Hmph, you're so carefree. I thought you'd be more flustered by now."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x195,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Well, I was pretty flustered until I came here."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "But, looking out at the scenery from here calmed me down a bit."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "I'm worried about Nio, but I figured that getting too flustered wouldn't be good, either."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Well, it's just as you say. So, the act of idly looking out at the sky had some beneficial effects..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "It's such a beautiful view, it'd be a waste if I don't enjoy it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0xe1,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Beautiful... Do you know how this big valley came into existence?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "No... It wasn't a beautiful valley to begin with?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0xe3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "It was not. The land around here was rich with a lot of different special ores and rare metals."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "And, it was filled with the spirits who dwelled within them. From that, such fantastic scenery opened up."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "That's what was recorded in the literature. That was only about a few hundred years ago."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "The remains of what was left after everything was snatched away...that's the scenery that you're looking at."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "Snatched away...? B-By who?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x91,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "By humans, of course. Shaving down the ground in pursuit of resources...their techniques of destruction are admirable."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x92,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "Although, it may be proof of the big possibilities of alchemy..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x93,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "For anyone who knows what this valley used to look like, it'd probably be a heartrending sight."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "Something like that really happened?<CR>I never even knew..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "However, it's interesting that to you, not knowing its history, this scenery appears to be beautiful."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "I consider beauty to be something that dwells in nature, and yet..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x17,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "Things that were devastated by human hands might be part of nature, as well."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc4,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "Past civilizations were really amazing. But they're kinda scary..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc5,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "Are ancient skills really magnificent? Or..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0xe1,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "msg_string": "How past alchemy contributed to the world's development, and lured it down the path to extinction..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0xe2,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x1c,
            "msg_string": "Following those footprints is one of the goals of my journey."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0xe2,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x1d,
            "msg_string": "Whether it's with stone implements or alchemy, what humans do never changes."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0xe2,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x1e,
            "msg_string": "One thing I can say is...turning a simple mistake into something irreversible is the history of alchemy."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc5,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1f,
            "msg_string": "(Mr. Keith... He seems kinda sad...)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc6,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x20,
            "msg_string": "Alchemy might've destroyed some<CR>things..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x21,
            "msg_string": "But I'm sure it's done a lot of good for people, too."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x22,
            "msg_string": "Like healing the sick, fixing broken things, and making life more convenient..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x23,
            "msg_string": "I'm sure it's done lots of good things..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x6,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x24,
            "msg_string": "Plus, alchemy can save Nio, too, right?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0xe3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x25,
            "msg_string": "There is that side to it. However, they're two sides of the same coin."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x26,
            "msg_string": "The current state of the world shows which side is winning. With the path we're on, we'll soon be..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x91,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x27,
            "msg_string": "On the verge of extinction."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc4,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x28,
            "msg_string": "What...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x92,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x29,
            "msg_string": "Dig just a little down into a lifeless wasteland and you'll find toxic materials..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x92,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x2a,
            "msg_string": "Water sources are disappearing, making it harder to secure drinking water..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x92,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x2b,
            "msg_string": "It's proof that a disaster happened in the past that greatly exceeded nature's ability to heal."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc5,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x2c,
            "msg_string": "That's..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x93,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2d,
            "msg_string": "I'm sure you'll eventually understand. Now, I guess it's time for me to go."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x15,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2e,
            "msg_string": "We'll continue this conversation next time. Farewell."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc5,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x2f,
            "msg_string": "(For such a terrible thing to happen to the world in the past...)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc5,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x30,
            "msg_string": "(I guess I don't know anything about alchemy yet...)"
        }
    ]
}